snippet.title: Simply Explained
snippet.description:
Taking complicated topics and explaining them in plain English. 

My name is Xavier. I’m very passionate about all kinds of technologies and I love taking complex topics and explaining them in a simple and straightforward way. It’s this passion that got me into making YouTube videos.

With this channel, I hope to pass along some of my knowledge to others. Let me know if you have suggestions for future videos or improvements.
